super-csv-annotation 1.0.3 API

パッケージ 
パッケージ 説明
org.supercsv.ext  
org.supercsv.ext.annotation
Provides Super CSV annotations.
org.supercsv.ext.builder
Provides the building chain CellProcessor classes from CsvBean's annotation.
org.supercsv.ext.cellprocessor
Provides CellProcessor classes for conversion, formatting and parsing.
org.supercsv.ext.cellprocessor.constraint
Provides CellProcessor classes for enforcing constraints.
org.supercsv.ext.cellprocessor.ift
Provides CellProcessor interfaces, used to control/restrict how processors can be chained together
org.supercsv.ext.exception
Provides the exceptions that may be thrown by Super CSV.
org.supercsv.ext.io
Provides the various readers and writers used to read/write Strings, Maps, or Objects.
org.supercsv.ext.localization
Provides convert and localize messages classes.
